OL,3,CStudent loan interest rates to be
OL,4,Ccapped at 6% for plan 2 and 3 borrowers
OL,6,FInterest on Plan 2 and 3 student loans
OL,7,Fwill be capped at 6%, the government
OL,8,Fhas announced in a bid to ease
OL,9,Fpressure on graduates with mounting
OL,10,Frepayments.
OL,12,FThe measure, affecting students and
OL,13,Fgraduates in England and Wales, will
OL,14,Fcome into force from September 1, and
OL,15,Fwill replace the current cap of RPI+3%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
