OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775596265
OL,3,CStudent loan interest rates to be
OL,4,Ccapped at 6% for plan 2 and 3 borrowers
OL,6,FMinisters say the reform will protect
OL,7,FPlan 2 and 3 borrowers from any short-
OL,8,Fterm increases in RPI due to global
OL,9,Fshocks, such as temporary spikes in
OL,10,Foil prices following the outbreak of
OL,11,Fthe war in Iran.
OL,13,FMinister for Skills, Jacqui Smith,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We know that the conflict in
OL,15,Fthe Middle East is causing anxiety at
OL,16,Fhome, and while the risk of global
OL,17,Fshocks is beyond our control,
OL,18,Fprotecting people here is not.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775596265
OL,3,CStudent loan interest rates to be
OL,4,Ccapped at 6% for plan 2 and 3 borrowers
OL,6,F"Capping the maximum interest rate on
OL,7,FPlan 2 and Plan 3 student loans will
OL,8,Fprovide immediate protection for
OL,9,Fborrowers, supporting those who are
OL,10,Fmost exposed within this already
OL,11,Funfair system.
OL,13,F"We're acting now to defend against
OL,14,Fthe consequences of far-away conflicts
OL,15,Fin an uncertain world. More broadly,
OL,16,Fwe're bringing back maintenance grants
OL,17,Fand continuing to look at the broken
OL,18,FPlan 2 system we inherited, and the
OL,19,Fwider student finance system, to make
OL,20,Fit fairer for students, graduates and
OL,21,Ftaxpayers."
