OL,3,CStudent loan interest rates to be
OL,4,Ccapped at 6% for plan 2 and 3 borrowers
OL,6,FThe measure is part of government
OL,7,Fplans to ease cost-of-living pressures
OL,8,Ffollowing the outbreak of conflict in
OL,9,Fthe Middle East, including a #53
OL,10,Fmillion fund to help those who rely on
OL,11,Fheating oil.
