OL,3,CStudent loan interest rates to be
OL,4,Ccapped at 6% for plan 2 and 3 borrowers
OL,6,FPlan 2 student loans are those taken
OL,7,Fout for undergraduate courses and
OL,8,FPostgraduate Certificates of Education
OL,9,F(PGCE) since September 1, 2012 in
OL,10,FWales and between September 1, 2012
OL,11,Fand July 31, 2023 in England.
OL,13,FPlan 3 student loans cover
OL,14,Fpostgraduate master's or doctoral
OL,15,Fcourses for borrowers in England and
OL,16,FWales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
