OL,3,CStudent loan interest rates to be
OL,4,Ccapped at 6% for plan 2 and 3 borrowers
OL,6,FIn April 2025, the repayment threshold
OL,7,Ffor Plan 2 loans was increased to
OL,8,F#28,470 in April 2025 ` its first
OL,9,Fincrease since 2021 ` and is set to go
OL,10,Fup again this April, to #29,385.
